    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Alright, based on #378 here is the API I'm going for:\n\n``` js\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.currentRefinedValues({\n    container: '#current-refinements-list',\n    cssClasses: {root, header, body, clearAll, item, link, count, footer},\n    facets: [ // Optional, if not specified, takes all of the facets\n      { name: 'category'[, transformData: function (data) { /* ... */ return data; }]},\n      { name: 'brand'[, transformData: function (data) { /* ... */ return data; }]}\n    ],\n    templates: {\n      header: '',\n      item: '' + // Called with this.facets[current_facet.name].transformData({cssClasses, facetName, url, name, count})\n        '<a class=\"{{ cssClasses.link }}\" href=\"{{ url }}\">' +\n        '  {{ name }}' +\n        '  <span class=\"{{ cssClasses.count }}\">' +\n        '    {{ count }}' +\n        '  </span>' +\n        '</a>',\n      clearAll: '' +\n        '<a class=\"{{ cssClasses.clearAll }}\" href=\"{{ url }}\">' +\n        '  Clear all' +\n        '</a>',\n      footer: ''\n    },\n    clearAll: 'after', // [true, false, 'before', 'after'] (true == 'before')\n    hideContainerWhenNoRefinements: true\n  })\n);\n```\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-29T09:07:04Z",
